      <title>随着天然气库存下降，德国正在就天然气存储支持进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/germany-in-intense-talks-on-gas-storage-support-as-levels-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国天然气市场经理表示，由于欧洲正濒临另一场供应紧缩的边缘，其正在与当局“密切讨论”补充储存设施的潜在补贴问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-11/germany-in-intense-talks-on-gas-storage-support-as-levels-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 11:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
